1
00:00:18,582 --> 00:00:21,420
♪Wearing peach blossom makeup,
I boil tea over the stove♪

2
00:00:23,060 --> 00:00:25,780
♪With a pure heart,
I embroider the brocade of time♪

3
00:00:27,380 --> 00:00:31,380
♪On the short paper,
affection flows in the silent moonlight♪

4
00:00:31,820 --> 00:00:34,940
♪I only wish that by my side,
is my love♪

5
00:00:36,700 --> 00:00:39,940
♪Cool autumn wind blowing,
I gaze far leaning against the railing♪

6
00:00:41,620 --> 00:00:44,460
♪Sunset glow over the green hill,
in formation wild geese are flying♪

7
00:00:45,940 --> 00:00:50,020
♪Covering a thousand miles on horseback,
for whom is he longing♪

8
00:00:50,300 --> 00:00:53,620
♪He returned home in dreams♪

9
00:00:54,060 --> 00:00:58,220
♪I will never forget
that you held my hands♪

10
00:00:58,740 --> 00:01:03,020
♪In your warm palms
and we braved winds and waves♪

11
00:01:03,380 --> 00:01:08,300
♪Unexpectedly, after we traveled so far
and turned Grey-haired♪

12
00:01:08,580 --> 00:01:12,260
♪I am still by your side♪

13
00:01:12,740 --> 00:01:16,820
♪Hearts burning,
we look into each other's eyes♪

14
00:01:17,180 --> 00:01:21,500
♪Feelings overflowing,
they don't need to be hided♪

15
00:01:21,820 --> 00:01:26,500
♪No matter how time passes
and life changes♪

16
00:01:27,100 --> 00:01:31,060
♪Together, we will grow old♪

17
00:01:32,439 --> 00:01:36,331
=The Sword and the Brocade=

18
00:01:37,119 --> 00:01:39,250
=Episode 17=

19
00:01:41,160 --> 00:01:41,760
Your Ladyship.

20
00:01:41,960 --> 00:01:43,080
It's late.

21
00:01:43,200 --> 00:01:43,800
Should we prepare

22
00:01:43,920 --> 00:01:45,080
His Lordship's bath?

23
00:02:04,120 --> 00:02:07,920
Should we or should we not?

24
00:02:18,280 --> 00:02:19,480
Rest early then.

25
00:02:19,640 --> 00:02:20,400
I won't bother you.

26
00:02:21,120 --> 00:02:22,120
You're not bothering me.

27
00:02:22,480 --> 00:02:23,920
I'll see you out.

28
00:02:27,640 --> 00:02:29,280
You're so happy for me to leave.

29
00:02:31,000 --> 00:02:31,800
No.

30
00:02:32,240 --> 00:02:33,000
I'm just thinking

31
00:02:33,120 --> 00:02:34,800
that you're busy with work.

32
00:02:35,200 --> 00:02:37,280
I can't make you stay long.

33
00:02:41,680 --> 00:02:44,040
Yes, I'm busy with work.

34
00:02:46,120 --> 00:02:47,160
Take care, My Lord.

35
00:02:54,600 --> 00:02:56,200
Your Ladyship, weren't you
and His Lordship

36
00:02:56,320 --> 00:02:57,400
chatting so nicely just now?

37
00:02:57,520 --> 00:02:58,960
Why won't you let him
stay overnight?

38
00:02:59,080 --> 00:03:00,040
Right, Your Ladyship.

39
00:03:00,160 --> 00:03:01,080
Dongqing is right.

40
00:03:01,240 --> 00:03:03,120
After all, you've already married
into the Xu family.

41
00:03:03,240 --> 00:03:05,280
If you and His Lordship's relationship

42
00:03:05,400 --> 00:03:06,040
don't get improved,

43
00:03:06,160 --> 00:03:07,680
this can't go on for long.

44
00:03:08,360 --> 00:03:09,840
Don't worry about it.

45
00:03:10,120 --> 00:03:11,160
I know what to do.

46
00:03:24,120 --> 00:03:25,080
My Lord.

47
00:03:32,680 --> 00:03:33,640
Didn't I tell you already?

48
00:03:33,760 --> 00:03:34,520
I must finish working

49
00:03:34,600 --> 00:03:35,880
on the documents tonight.

50
00:03:36,200 --> 00:03:37,320
Why did you put them away?

51
00:03:38,520 --> 00:03:39,760
I heard that you

52
00:03:39,840 --> 00:03:40,920
would stay in Western Lateral Court,

53
00:03:41,120 --> 00:03:42,720
so I thought you
wouldn't be back tonight.

54
00:03:42,840 --> 00:03:44,120
I'm not done with my work yet.

55
00:03:44,240 --> 00:03:45,600
Why would I stay
in Western Lateral Court?

56
00:03:48,320 --> 00:03:49,640
-Could Her Ladyship...
-You're still asking questions?

57
00:04:22,760 --> 00:04:23,280
Madam.

58
00:04:23,440 --> 00:04:25,120
His Lordship didn't stay
in Western Lateral Court.

59
00:04:25,240 --> 00:04:26,280
He went back to his place.

60
00:04:28,320 --> 00:04:29,360
It seems like

61
00:04:29,520 --> 00:04:31,320
even if Her Ladyship is managing
the household affairs,

62
00:04:31,480 --> 00:04:33,520
she still didn't get His Lordship's favor.

63
00:04:35,320 --> 00:04:36,240
This time,

64
00:04:36,360 --> 00:04:37,240
I defeated

65
00:04:37,360 --> 00:04:38,960
Concubine Qiao effortlessly.

66
00:04:39,360 --> 00:04:40,080
In the future,

67
00:04:40,200 --> 00:04:41,400
I must win over

68
00:04:41,520 --> 00:04:42,720
Her Ladyship.

69
00:04:43,280 --> 00:04:44,720
The Wen family

70
00:04:44,840 --> 00:04:46,000
can overturn its situation soon.

71
00:04:46,440 --> 00:04:48,080
Last time, she received
20 tael of silver,

72
00:04:48,200 --> 00:04:49,560
and she was so happy.

73
00:04:49,640 --> 00:04:50,920
She should be very easy to deal with.

74
00:04:52,320 --> 00:04:54,680
She's still an illegitimate daughter
after all.

75
00:04:55,400 --> 00:04:57,440
Even if she's managing
the household affairs now,

76
00:04:57,760 --> 00:04:58,320
she still

77
00:04:58,400 --> 00:04:59,880
hasn't seen much of the world.

78
00:05:06,080 --> 00:05:06,960
Here, Madam.

79
00:05:07,840 --> 00:05:08,840
More or less, we all

80
00:05:08,920 --> 00:05:10,120
have looked down on and offended
Her Ladyship.

81
00:05:10,200 --> 00:05:10,960
I wonder

82
00:05:11,080 --> 00:05:12,440
how she'll deal with us.

83
00:05:12,520 --> 00:05:13,960
Right.

84
00:05:14,840 --> 00:05:16,320
What are you worried about?

85
00:05:16,520 --> 00:05:18,080
Her Ladyship just started managing
the household affairs.

86
00:05:18,200 --> 00:05:19,400
She doesn't know anything.

87
00:05:19,920 --> 00:05:22,040
It's the time for her to win us over.

88
00:05:22,440 --> 00:05:24,160
Besides, last night,

89
00:05:24,280 --> 00:05:26,040
His Lordship went to her court,
then left.

90
00:05:26,640 --> 00:05:27,640
It's obvious that Her Ladyship

91
00:05:27,800 --> 00:05:30,000
doesn't have His Lordship's
favor at all.

92
00:05:31,320 --> 00:05:32,840
She wouldn't dare to do anything.

93
00:05:33,360 --> 00:05:34,520
Seriously?

94
00:05:35,400 --> 00:05:37,400
Everyone, please follow me.

95
00:05:53,920 --> 00:05:54,680
Mrs. Li.

96
00:05:55,279 --> 00:05:55,800
Yes.

97
00:05:56,600 --> 00:05:58,160
You manage the maids

98
00:05:58,279 --> 00:05:58,880
and servants in the mansion.

99
00:05:58,959 --> 00:06:00,440
Their dispatch, monthly salaries,

100
00:06:00,520 --> 00:06:02,800
and rewards and punishments are clearly
recorded in the accounting books.

101
00:06:03,160 --> 00:06:04,360
I'm rewarding you
with two tael of silver.

102
00:06:04,800 --> 00:06:06,120
Thank you, Your Ladyship.

103
00:06:08,640 --> 00:06:09,480
Thank you.

104
00:06:11,080 --> 00:06:11,800
Mrs. Wang.

105
00:06:14,080 --> 00:06:15,520
You're in charge of the purchasing
in the kitchen.

106
00:06:15,960 --> 00:06:17,160
In the accounting books,

107
00:06:17,280 --> 00:06:18,920
for the kitchen's monthly expenses,

108
00:06:19,000 --> 00:06:20,360
the prices of the stores you bought from

109
00:06:20,520 --> 00:06:21,880
for expensive food items

110
00:06:22,000 --> 00:06:23,760
such as ginseng and bird's nest

111
00:06:23,880 --> 00:06:25,680
are 30 percent higher
compared to other stores.

112
00:06:26,520 --> 00:06:27,720
What is going on?

113
00:06:28,000 --> 00:06:29,520
Your Ladyship is unaware.

114
00:06:29,760 --> 00:06:31,800
Their items

115
00:06:31,960 --> 00:06:34,200
are much better than the other stores'.

116
00:06:34,480 --> 00:06:35,680
In that case,

117
00:06:35,840 --> 00:06:37,480
do you dare to compare the items you got

118
00:06:37,600 --> 00:06:39,320
with the other stores'?

119
00:06:39,920 --> 00:06:40,440
Well...

120
00:06:41,240 --> 00:06:42,000
Mrs. Zhou.

121
00:06:44,320 --> 00:06:45,680
You're in charge

122
00:06:45,800 --> 00:06:47,840
of the silk, satin, and clothing
for four seasons.

123
00:06:48,120 --> 00:06:49,200
You decide

124
00:06:49,360 --> 00:06:50,600
which embroidery shop

125
00:06:50,760 --> 00:06:52,200
and which thread shop to buy from.

126
00:06:52,760 --> 00:06:53,840
Do you want me to calculate

127
00:06:54,000 --> 00:06:54,840
all the kickbacks

128
00:06:54,960 --> 00:06:56,320
you got from them?

129
00:06:56,320 --> 00:06:56,840
Your Ladyship.

130
00:06:57,520 --> 00:06:58,520
Your... Your Ladyship.

131
00:06:59,000 --> 00:07:00,280
You don't have any proof of that.

132
00:07:00,400 --> 00:07:01,800
You can't speak irresponsibly.

133
00:07:02,280 --> 00:07:03,400
I can't take the responsibility

134
00:07:03,560 --> 00:07:04,880
for that charge.

135
00:07:05,440 --> 00:07:06,640
Speak irresponsibly?

136
00:07:10,360 --> 00:07:12,040
Even if I haven't managed
household affairs before,

137
00:07:12,520 --> 00:07:14,480
I was poor when I was little.

138
00:07:14,920 --> 00:07:16,080
I must calculate

139
00:07:16,240 --> 00:07:17,280
each needle, thread,

140
00:07:17,480 --> 00:07:19,120
fabric, and clothing I spend on.

141
00:07:19,920 --> 00:07:21,280
If you think

142
00:07:21,400 --> 00:07:22,440
that I am the daughter

143
00:07:22,560 --> 00:07:24,440
of an eminent family,

144
00:07:24,680 --> 00:07:26,200
who is pampered and doesn't know

145
00:07:26,360 --> 00:07:27,600
how to read accounting books,

146
00:07:27,880 --> 00:07:29,120
you're wrong.

147
00:07:29,920 --> 00:07:31,000
You two

148
00:07:31,320 --> 00:07:34,040
deceived your masters and deluded
your subordinates to fill your pockets.

149
00:07:34,880 --> 00:07:36,600
Since you've been working
in the Xu family for a long time,

150
00:07:36,760 --> 00:07:38,120
I can let bygones be bygones.

151
00:07:38,400 --> 00:07:40,160
But starting today,

152
00:07:40,520 --> 00:07:41,800
let others

153
00:07:41,960 --> 00:07:43,480
do your jobs.

154
00:07:43,680 --> 00:07:44,320
Your Ladyship.

155
00:07:44,520 --> 00:07:46,040
Wait a minute.

156
00:07:46,240 --> 00:07:47,960
Without the two of us,

157
00:07:48,080 --> 00:07:49,840
won't the Xu family
fall into chaos then?

158
00:07:50,520 --> 00:07:51,960
I've already arranged for new people

159
00:07:52,040 --> 00:07:53,120
to take the positions

160
00:07:53,280 --> 00:07:54,760
you were occupying.

161
00:07:55,400 --> 00:07:57,360
Whether the family will fall
into chaos or not

162
00:07:57,520 --> 00:07:59,480
isn't your concern anymore.

163
00:07:59,920 --> 00:08:00,800
Your Ladyship.

164
00:08:01,440 --> 00:08:03,240
Please be kind.

165
00:08:03,640 --> 00:08:04,160
I'm already kind enough

166
00:08:04,280 --> 00:08:05,560
not to punish you.

167
00:08:05,680 --> 00:08:07,400
If you can't accept it,

168
00:08:07,560 --> 00:08:08,360
we can all go

169
00:08:08,480 --> 00:08:09,880
and speak to Great Madam.

170
00:08:11,200 --> 00:08:11,920
Well...

171
00:08:16,360 --> 00:08:17,480
Everyone.

172
00:08:17,720 --> 00:08:18,760
You may go.

173
00:08:20,080 --> 00:08:20,560
I...

174
00:08:24,120 --> 00:08:24,800
Let's go.

175
00:08:33,040 --> 00:08:34,000
Your Ladyship, look.

176
00:08:35,320 --> 00:08:36,760
These are the records of the fabrics

177
00:08:36,880 --> 00:08:37,880
that went out from the warehouse.

178
00:08:40,040 --> 00:08:41,880
If not for the convenience
of our investigation,

179
00:08:42,120 --> 00:08:42,680
I don't want

180
00:08:42,800 --> 00:08:43,520
to do the thankless task

181
00:08:43,640 --> 00:08:45,000
of managing household affairs.

182
00:08:45,440 --> 00:08:46,600
With these,

183
00:08:46,720 --> 00:08:47,320
can we really find clues

184
00:08:47,480 --> 00:08:48,760
about that embroidery fabric?

185
00:08:49,240 --> 00:08:51,120
Since there was a similar fabric
in the villa,

186
00:08:51,280 --> 00:08:52,440
we just need to find out

187
00:08:52,600 --> 00:08:53,360
who have

188
00:08:53,520 --> 00:08:54,920
used these fabrics

189
00:08:55,000 --> 00:08:56,120
before last year's Dragon Boat Festival,

190
00:08:56,680 --> 00:08:58,120
then follow the clues,

191
00:08:58,400 --> 00:08:59,520
and we can surely find something.

192
00:09:07,560 --> 00:09:08,400
How strange.

193
00:09:08,960 --> 00:09:10,200
What's the matter, Your Ladyship?

194
00:09:10,480 --> 00:09:11,360
There's a record of purchasing

195
00:09:11,520 --> 00:09:13,560
huge amounts of silk and satin
in the household.

196
00:09:14,800 --> 00:09:16,720
It was when Yuanniang was still alive.

197
00:09:17,760 --> 00:09:19,000
Since Concubine Qiao

198
00:09:19,600 --> 00:09:20,400
started managing the household affairs,

199
00:09:20,400 --> 00:09:21,960
she started buying

200
00:09:22,240 --> 00:09:22,920
the silk and satin

201
00:09:23,080 --> 00:09:25,040
from Zhang's Silk and Satin.

202
00:09:25,840 --> 00:09:26,520
This is

203
00:09:26,640 --> 00:09:28,000
not a small expense.

204
00:09:28,480 --> 00:09:29,880
Didn't the Wen family

205
00:09:30,040 --> 00:09:32,720
lose a lot of money then?

206
00:09:34,200 --> 00:09:35,920
Based on Concubine Wen's personality,

207
00:09:36,080 --> 00:09:37,560
she surely wouldn't just take that.

208
00:09:37,840 --> 00:09:39,080
Would Concubine Wen

209
00:09:39,240 --> 00:09:40,520
take revenge against
Concubine Qiao then?

210
00:09:42,160 --> 00:09:43,560
I'm afraid she already did.

211
00:09:48,000 --> 00:09:49,280
Forget it. Let's not mind her first.

212
00:09:49,440 --> 00:09:50,320
Let's continue checking.

213
00:09:54,920 --> 00:09:55,640
I found it.

214
00:09:55,840 --> 00:09:56,440
Take a look.

215
00:09:57,280 --> 00:09:58,120
It... It says here

216
00:09:58,280 --> 00:09:59,360
that during the Dragon Boat Festival
last year,

217
00:09:59,560 --> 00:10:00,120
Princess Danyang,

218
00:10:00,280 --> 00:10:01,320
Concubine Wen, and Concubine Qiao

219
00:10:01,480 --> 00:10:03,400
took those fabrics.

220
00:10:05,040 --> 00:10:05,800
That means

221
00:10:05,960 --> 00:10:06,520
the killer

222
00:10:06,640 --> 00:10:07,960
should have something to do with them.

223
00:10:08,360 --> 00:10:09,760
Who could it be then?

224
00:10:10,600 --> 00:10:12,120
But this kind of fabric

225
00:10:12,280 --> 00:10:13,559
isn't the type of grand fabric

226
00:10:13,679 --> 00:10:14,600
that women like.

227
00:10:14,760 --> 00:10:16,360
It's more suitable
to make an inner garment

228
00:10:16,480 --> 00:10:17,559
or perfume satchels and the like.

229
00:10:19,440 --> 00:10:20,679
During the Dragon Boat Festival,

230
00:10:20,840 --> 00:10:21,840
women would usually make

231
00:10:22,000 --> 00:10:23,720
perfume satchels for the one they love.

232
00:10:24,640 --> 00:10:26,080
The one they love?

233
00:10:26,280 --> 00:10:28,360
His Lordship and Master Lingkuan?

234
00:10:28,520 --> 00:10:29,360
Right.

235
00:10:29,520 --> 00:10:30,760
We never found any clues

236
00:10:30,880 --> 00:10:32,120
from the female members
of the family before.

237
00:10:32,280 --> 00:10:33,440
Perhaps we can find something
through His Lordship

238
00:10:33,600 --> 00:10:35,280
and Master Lingkuan.

239
00:10:36,720 --> 00:10:37,280
If we can find

240
00:10:37,400 --> 00:10:38,760
the items that they gave out,

241
00:10:39,080 --> 00:10:40,600
we can surely find some clues

242
00:10:40,800 --> 00:10:41,640
to know who the real killer is.

243
00:10:42,920 --> 00:10:44,840
I noticed that the wisdom
of three ordinary people

244
00:10:45,000 --> 00:10:46,320
can outwit a genius.

245
00:10:46,480 --> 00:10:48,400
I'm not ordinary.

246
00:10:49,080 --> 00:10:50,240
You are.

247
00:10:57,520 --> 00:10:58,000
My Lord.

248
00:10:58,120 --> 00:10:59,720
Are you going to bathe here tonight?

249
00:11:13,240 --> 00:11:15,240
Your Ladyship, it's late.

250
00:11:15,360 --> 00:11:16,000
Should we prepare

251
00:11:16,080 --> 00:11:17,280
His Lordship's bath?

252
00:11:31,720 --> 00:11:33,040
Why are you so clumsy?

253
00:11:33,240 --> 00:11:34,920
Don't you see that I'm working?

254
00:11:35,840 --> 00:11:37,560
I'm sorry, my hand slipped.

255
00:11:38,680 --> 00:11:39,320
Never mind.

256
00:11:39,720 --> 00:11:40,640
Grind the ink for me.

257
00:11:56,600 --> 00:11:58,160
Why did you add so much water?

258
00:11:58,800 --> 00:12:00,160
My writing will bleed at the edges.

259
00:12:04,440 --> 00:12:05,480
My Lord, if you think

260
00:12:05,640 --> 00:12:06,720
that I'm not serving you well,

261
00:12:06,920 --> 00:12:07,760
I

262
00:12:07,920 --> 00:12:09,680
will find a meticulous maid
to serve you.

263
00:12:15,040 --> 00:12:16,640
All right, you're tired too.

264
00:12:16,840 --> 00:12:17,680
Go and rest.

265
00:12:19,200 --> 00:12:20,360
Yes, My Lord.

266
00:12:30,800 --> 00:12:31,800
General Fu.

267
00:12:32,720 --> 00:12:34,760
General Fu, why are you here?

268
00:12:35,520 --> 00:12:36,320
His Lordship is in a bad mood.

269
00:12:36,480 --> 00:12:37,400
He kept getting angry.

270
00:12:37,680 --> 00:12:39,520
I can't do my job anymore.

271
00:12:39,920 --> 00:12:41,720
General Fu, if it's not urgent,

272
00:12:42,160 --> 00:12:43,480
don't go inside.

273
00:12:44,680 --> 00:12:46,480
I don't have any urgent matters.

274
00:12:47,080 --> 00:12:47,720
But why is His Lordship

275
00:12:47,880 --> 00:12:49,000
in a bad mood?

276
00:12:52,400 --> 00:12:53,920
Two days ago, he came back
from Western Lateral Court

277
00:12:54,080 --> 00:12:55,040
and became this way.

278
00:12:55,200 --> 00:12:56,080
Western Lateral Court?

279
00:12:57,080 --> 00:12:58,160
It's related to Her Ladyship?

280
00:12:58,600 --> 00:12:59,920
His Lordship is angry at Her Ladyship?

281
00:13:03,000 --> 00:13:05,000
I don't dare to gossip
behind His Lordship's back

282
00:13:05,120 --> 00:13:06,680
about his affairs with Her Lordship.

283
00:13:08,160 --> 00:13:09,680
You won't tell me the whole story.

284
00:13:11,080 --> 00:13:11,960
That's so annoying.

285
00:13:30,160 --> 00:13:31,040
I suddenly remember that I forgot

286
00:13:31,160 --> 00:13:32,120
to instruct the kitchen about something.

287
00:13:32,280 --> 00:13:32,880
Wait for me.

288
00:13:33,040 --> 00:13:34,120
I'll be right back.

289
00:13:38,080 --> 00:13:39,480
She always says that I'm careless.

290
00:13:39,680 --> 00:13:40,960
She's the same.

291
00:13:58,000 --> 00:13:59,200
(Let me scare Amber.)

292
00:14:27,120 --> 00:14:27,840
General Fu.

293
00:14:28,040 --> 00:14:29,120
Why is it you?

294
00:14:29,280 --> 00:14:30,320
I'm the one who should ask you
that question.

295
00:14:30,520 --> 00:14:30,920
It's late at night.

296
00:14:31,040 --> 00:14:31,400
Why are you

297
00:14:31,560 --> 00:14:32,360
sneaking around here?

298
00:14:32,560 --> 00:14:33,760
You're the one who's sneaking around.

299
00:14:33,920 --> 00:14:34,840
This is the Mansion of Xu.

300
00:14:35,000 --> 00:14:36,160
Why are you here so late at night?

301
00:14:36,360 --> 00:14:37,240
Hey.

302
00:14:37,440 --> 00:14:38,840
Instead of admitting your mistake,
you're accusing me.

303
00:14:39,280 --> 00:14:40,040
And are you a dog?

304
00:14:40,200 --> 00:14:41,200
Why did you bite me?

305
00:14:41,360 --> 00:14:42,160
You're the dog.

306
00:14:42,320 --> 00:14:43,640
You flung yourself at me.

307
00:14:43,800 --> 00:14:45,360
You're at fault,
and you won't apologize.

308
00:14:45,560 --> 00:14:46,560
You're even being so stubborn.

309
00:14:46,720 --> 00:14:47,800
If you want to blame me,

310
00:14:47,920 --> 00:14:48,560
go and tell Her Ladyship

311
00:14:48,720 --> 00:14:49,640
about me.

312
00:14:51,560 --> 00:14:52,280
There's no need.

313
00:14:52,800 --> 00:14:53,960
I won't argue

314
00:14:54,160 --> 00:14:55,080
with a girl.

315
00:14:55,240 --> 00:14:56,080
However,

316
00:14:56,240 --> 00:14:57,760
don't tell anyone about this.

317
00:15:00,520 --> 00:15:01,960
Are you scared

318
00:15:02,120 --> 00:15:03,440
that if people find out

319
00:15:03,600 --> 00:15:04,760
that you got scared because of me,

320
00:15:04,920 --> 00:15:06,800
it will ruin your reputation?

321
00:15:07,120 --> 00:15:07,880
That's nonsense.

322
00:15:08,040 --> 00:15:09,080
You didn't scare me.

323
00:15:09,200 --> 00:15:10,680
Then why did you shout just now?

324
00:15:11,160 --> 00:15:11,640
I...

325
00:15:13,080 --> 00:15:14,200
I shouted

326
00:15:15,080 --> 00:15:16,560
because I was directing my qi
to a part of my body.

327
00:15:17,240 --> 00:15:18,440
The qi of those who practice martial arts
is in the diaphragm.

328
00:15:18,640 --> 00:15:19,400
Don't you know that?

329
00:15:19,560 --> 00:15:20,640
You won't get it even if I told you.

330
00:15:20,920 --> 00:15:21,840
Dongqing.

331
00:15:23,160 --> 00:15:23,480
Dongqing.

332
00:15:23,480 --> 00:15:23,800
I'll go ahead.

333
00:15:24,000 --> 00:15:24,720
Don't tell anyone about it.

334
00:15:24,920 --> 00:15:25,880
Otherwise, I won't spare you.

335
00:15:29,040 --> 00:15:29,960
Dongqing.

336
00:15:35,520 --> 00:15:37,200
Who were you talking to just now?

337
00:15:38,200 --> 00:15:39,320
No one.

338
00:15:40,200 --> 00:15:40,920
A dog.

339
00:15:41,080 --> 00:15:42,280
A dog ran by.

340
00:15:42,400 --> 00:15:43,200
A dog?

341
00:15:43,360 --> 00:15:44,680
Our yard has a dog again?

342
00:15:44,840 --> 00:15:45,720
No.

343
00:15:45,960 --> 00:15:47,440
It's too dark. I didn't see it clearly.

344
00:15:47,600 --> 00:15:49,560
Perhaps it was a cat.

345
00:15:50,240 --> 00:15:51,280
A scaredy cat.

346
00:15:51,440 --> 00:15:52,120
All right.

347
00:15:52,280 --> 00:15:53,160
Let's go back.

348
00:15:53,280 --> 00:15:54,520
Her Ladyship should be hungry.

349
00:16:21,680 --> 00:16:22,600
Why are you here?

350
00:16:22,920 --> 00:16:24,840
I made some pastries and soup

351
00:16:25,000 --> 00:16:26,640
to nourish you, My Lord.

352
00:16:27,480 --> 00:16:28,040
Place them over there.

353
00:16:45,280 --> 00:16:46,720
My Lord, what are you reading?

354
00:16:47,760 --> 00:16:50,240
I'm writing a report
to comfort the refugees.

355
00:16:51,560 --> 00:16:53,920
I've heard that the refugees
often gather together

356
00:16:54,160 --> 00:16:55,520
and cause troubles.

357
00:16:55,920 --> 00:16:56,560
What if

358
00:16:56,720 --> 00:16:58,040
we move them out of the city
as soon as we can,

359
00:16:58,200 --> 00:17:00,400
and let them stay in a nearby village?

360
00:17:01,080 --> 00:17:02,080
There's flooding everywhere.

361
00:17:02,480 --> 00:17:04,160
The villages can't accommodate
so many people.

362
00:17:04,400 --> 00:17:05,560
I'm afraid there will be casualties.

363
00:17:06,520 --> 00:17:08,960
Natural disasters and man-made
misfortunes are unavoidable.

364
00:17:09,160 --> 00:17:09,920
It's better than letting them stay
in the capital,

365
00:17:09,920 --> 00:17:11,240
creating bigger trouble,

366
00:17:11,440 --> 00:17:12,800
and infuriating His Majesty.

367
00:17:15,040 --> 00:17:16,320
How can the lives of those citizens

368
00:17:16,520 --> 00:17:18,680
compare to your future?

369
00:17:27,160 --> 00:17:27,920
My Lord.

370
00:17:28,400 --> 00:17:29,520
The soup will get cold.

371
00:17:29,720 --> 00:17:30,960
Drink it while it's hot.

372
00:17:31,920 --> 00:17:32,600
Lately,

373
00:17:32,800 --> 00:17:34,080
Mother's been having leg pains again.

374
00:17:34,280 --> 00:17:35,440
I'm going to visit her.

375
00:17:37,400 --> 00:17:38,240
What a coincidence.

376
00:17:38,400 --> 00:17:39,480
I made a pair of knee pads,

377
00:17:39,640 --> 00:17:40,840
and I wanted to bring it to her.

378
00:17:43,920 --> 00:17:44,560
Let's go then.

379
00:17:45,400 --> 00:17:46,000
Yes.

380
00:17:48,760 --> 00:17:49,480
Great Madam.

381
00:17:49,680 --> 00:17:51,520
I made these knee pads for you.

382
00:17:56,200 --> 00:17:58,400
Look at you two.

383
00:17:58,800 --> 00:17:59,800
You're so concerned

384
00:18:00,000 --> 00:18:01,960
about my health.

385
00:18:03,360 --> 00:18:04,720
It's what I should do.

386
00:18:06,920 --> 00:18:09,800
Before, I made a mistake,

387
00:18:10,040 --> 00:18:11,680
and you didn't blame me.

388
00:18:11,840 --> 00:18:13,520
I'm lucky.

389
00:18:14,240 --> 00:18:16,480
I should be filial to you.

390
00:18:17,160 --> 00:18:19,080
Originally, I was worried

391
00:18:19,240 --> 00:18:20,800
that you'd feel bad

392
00:18:20,960 --> 00:18:22,800
because of the management
of household affairs.

393
00:18:23,280 --> 00:18:25,160
Now, I see it.

394
00:18:26,440 --> 00:18:27,760
I see that you are

395
00:18:27,920 --> 00:18:30,720
broad-minded.

396
00:18:31,880 --> 00:18:33,000
Lingyi.

397
00:18:33,520 --> 00:18:34,720
You must take care

398
00:18:34,880 --> 00:18:36,440
of Lianfang more.

399
00:18:40,200 --> 00:18:41,880
I'm sorry to worry you, Great Madam.

400
00:18:42,520 --> 00:18:45,400
Aside from you,

401
00:18:45,599 --> 00:18:46,920
His Lordship is my priority.

402
00:18:47,319 --> 00:18:49,079
I think about him every moment
of every day.

403
00:18:50,680 --> 00:18:52,280
What a good child.

404
00:18:54,480 --> 00:18:55,480
However,

405
00:18:55,680 --> 00:18:57,560
don't always think about me.

406
00:18:57,920 --> 00:18:59,280
Think more

407
00:18:59,480 --> 00:19:02,960
about how to give descendants
to the Xu family.

408
00:19:05,760 --> 00:19:06,880
Lingyi.

409
00:19:07,040 --> 00:19:08,240
Don't just be busy

410
00:19:08,400 --> 00:19:10,400
with work all day.

411
00:19:10,800 --> 00:19:12,400
You must think of Lianfang

412
00:19:12,600 --> 00:19:14,960
and visit her more.

413
00:19:26,600 --> 00:19:27,480
How is it?

414
00:19:27,800 --> 00:19:28,440
Your Ladyship.

415
00:19:28,720 --> 00:19:29,480
His Lordship and Concubine Qiao

416
00:19:29,680 --> 00:19:31,000
are in Great Madam's room now.

417
00:19:31,200 --> 00:19:31,840
At this hour,

418
00:19:32,040 --> 00:19:32,600
Great Madam will surely

419
00:19:32,760 --> 00:19:33,760
ask them to stay and eat.

420
00:19:34,720 --> 00:19:36,040
That's great. This way,

421
00:19:36,240 --> 00:19:38,000
we'll have enough time to do things.

422
00:19:38,560 --> 00:19:38,920
Let's go.

423
00:19:42,080 --> 00:19:42,640
This one

424
00:19:42,840 --> 00:19:44,240
is your favorite design.

425
00:19:44,440 --> 00:19:45,880
I embroidered it for three days.

426
00:19:48,000 --> 00:19:49,760
You spent so much effort on it.

427
00:19:49,960 --> 00:19:51,760
Look at these threads.

428
00:19:51,960 --> 00:19:53,840
They're lined up so well.

429
00:19:54,040 --> 00:19:54,560
Mother.

430
00:19:55,160 --> 00:19:56,880
Grand Secretary told me

431
00:19:57,040 --> 00:19:59,440
to present the disaster relief report
to His Majesty as soon as I can.

432
00:19:59,640 --> 00:20:00,720
I'll go ahead.

433
00:20:01,400 --> 00:20:02,280
Wait.

434
00:20:02,880 --> 00:20:04,680
It's meal time.

435
00:20:04,880 --> 00:20:06,400
You and Lianfang should stay

436
00:20:06,600 --> 00:20:07,640
and eat with me.

437
00:20:08,040 --> 00:20:09,200
It's livelier if more people are here,

438
00:20:09,400 --> 00:20:11,280
and it makes my food taste better.

439
00:20:12,200 --> 00:20:13,480
The disaster is a matter
of great urgency.

440
00:20:14,000 --> 00:20:15,600
I'll eat with you next time.

441
00:20:18,800 --> 00:20:20,600
How stubborn.

442
00:20:23,240 --> 00:20:24,320
Great Madam.

443
00:20:25,400 --> 00:20:26,040
Is His Lordship

444
00:20:26,240 --> 00:20:27,560
not willing to forgive me?

445
00:20:27,760 --> 00:20:29,400
Don't think that way.

446
00:20:30,120 --> 00:20:32,280
That's how he is.

447
00:20:34,240 --> 00:20:36,400
You must take more initiative.

448
00:20:39,640 --> 00:20:40,840
Yes, Great Madam.

449
00:20:48,280 --> 00:20:49,320
Your Ladyship, why are you here?

450
00:20:49,520 --> 00:20:50,960
His Lordship isn't here now.

451
00:20:51,680 --> 00:20:52,800
That's fine.

452
00:20:53,000 --> 00:20:53,880
I'm planning to make new clothes

453
00:20:54,080 --> 00:20:54,840
for His Lordship.

454
00:20:55,040 --> 00:20:56,520
I just need to get a sample.

455
00:20:57,000 --> 00:20:58,240
I see. Please come in.

456
00:21:40,600 --> 00:21:41,400
What are you looking at?

457
00:21:42,840 --> 00:21:43,600
My Lord.

458
00:21:44,400 --> 00:21:45,360
Aren't you eating

459
00:21:45,560 --> 00:21:47,000
at Great Madam's?

460
00:21:47,800 --> 00:21:49,080
I have work to do.

461
00:21:49,720 --> 00:21:51,640
My Lord, Her Ladyship is inside.

462
00:21:56,720 --> 00:21:57,640
Make a pot

463
00:21:57,840 --> 00:21:59,840
of jasmine flower tea from His Majesty.

464
00:22:01,320 --> 00:22:01,920
My Lord.

465
00:22:02,120 --> 00:22:02,840
Didn't you complain

466
00:22:03,080 --> 00:22:04,720
that it was too weak and sweet?

467
00:22:05,360 --> 00:22:06,240
Did I say that?

468
00:22:09,280 --> 00:22:10,720
Yes, My Lord.

469
00:22:15,000 --> 00:22:16,400
(Why aren't these the same?)

470
00:22:22,040 --> 00:22:23,000
What are you looking for?

471
00:22:28,600 --> 00:22:29,440
My Lord.

472
00:22:30,680 --> 00:22:31,560
I originally wanted to
make a few clothes

473
00:22:31,760 --> 00:22:32,640
for you,

474
00:22:32,840 --> 00:22:33,960
so I came to get a sample

475
00:22:34,200 --> 00:22:35,120
to get your size.

476
00:22:35,560 --> 00:22:36,560
Just let the embroiderer

477
00:22:36,760 --> 00:22:38,160
take care of such trivial matters.

478
00:22:39,280 --> 00:22:40,960
I'm being too nosy then.

479
00:22:41,080 --> 00:22:42,680
I won't disturb you.

480
00:22:49,840 --> 00:22:51,040
The old clothes' size

481
00:22:51,280 --> 00:22:52,480
might not be suitable anymore.

482
00:22:53,320 --> 00:22:54,600
Measure me directly.

483
00:22:58,280 --> 00:22:59,840
You're the one who didn't want me
to make one.

484
00:22:59,960 --> 00:23:01,400
Now, you want me to make one.

485
00:23:01,840 --> 00:23:03,200
Since you have a lot of time,

486
00:23:03,280 --> 00:23:04,320
it's also good

487
00:23:04,440 --> 00:23:06,160
for you to make a couple of clothes
to kill some time.

488
00:23:11,680 --> 00:23:12,680
Why are you still standing there?

489
00:23:13,240 --> 00:23:14,200
Hurry up.

490
00:23:22,640 --> 00:23:23,440
Yes.

491
00:24:09,160 --> 00:24:10,640
May I use your pen and paper?

492
00:24:11,320 --> 00:24:12,000
They're over there.

493
00:24:29,280 --> 00:24:31,739
(Chest Length)

494
00:24:33,320 --> 00:24:34,760
Your regular script in small characters
are nice.

495
00:24:35,360 --> 00:24:36,600
The thickness is just right.

496
00:24:37,120 --> 00:24:38,440
It's forceful and gentle
at the same time.

497
00:24:45,840 --> 00:24:46,600
Are you done with the measurements?

498
00:24:47,640 --> 00:24:48,480
Not yet.

499
00:25:21,320 --> 00:25:22,480
By the way, My Lord,

500
00:25:23,040 --> 00:25:25,480
how are the refugees now?

501
00:25:25,600 --> 00:25:26,320
Has the government found a way

502
00:25:26,440 --> 00:25:27,720
to make arrangements for them?

503
00:25:28,760 --> 00:25:30,760
I'm actually worrying about that now.

504
00:25:31,280 --> 00:25:32,360
It's easy with men.

505
00:25:32,960 --> 00:25:34,720
Now, pirates are still a problem.

506
00:25:34,840 --> 00:25:35,880
Banditry is still continuing.

507
00:25:36,360 --> 00:25:38,400
I'm planning to let them join the army.

508
00:25:38,720 --> 00:25:40,560
Not only can they fulfill the army needs
of the government,

509
00:25:40,760 --> 00:25:41,920
they can also get salaries

510
00:25:42,080 --> 00:25:43,680
to support their families.

511
00:25:44,160 --> 00:25:46,040
As for those who aren't willing
to join the army,

512
00:25:46,280 --> 00:25:48,320
they can learn some skills
with the artisans

513
00:25:48,600 --> 00:25:49,560
in the military.

514
00:25:50,880 --> 00:25:52,160
Give a man a fish and feed him for day;

515
00:25:52,360 --> 00:25:54,480
teach a man how to fish
and feed him for a lifetime.

516
00:25:54,840 --> 00:25:55,880
But it's not convenient

517
00:25:55,960 --> 00:25:57,800
to place women in the army.

518
00:25:58,640 --> 00:25:59,600
I can't think

519
00:25:59,760 --> 00:26:01,200
of a better arrangement for them
at the moment.

520
00:26:02,680 --> 00:26:03,360
My Lord.

521
00:26:03,480 --> 00:26:04,640
What if you recruit the female refugees

522
00:26:04,760 --> 00:26:06,040
to the embroidery workshops?

523
00:26:07,520 --> 00:26:08,480
Embroidery workshops?

524
00:26:09,480 --> 00:26:10,520
I heard from Master Jian

525
00:26:10,640 --> 00:26:11,520
that due to the disaster,

526
00:26:11,640 --> 00:26:13,560
there is a high demand
for cotton and linen.

527
00:26:13,760 --> 00:26:15,400
But there aren't enough staff
in the embroidery workshops.

528
00:26:15,520 --> 00:26:16,560
The demand exceeds the supply.

529
00:26:16,800 --> 00:26:18,680
What if we ask Master Jian

530
00:26:18,960 --> 00:26:19,840
of Xianling Pavilion

531
00:26:19,960 --> 00:26:21,040
to work with the major
embroidery workshops

532
00:26:21,120 --> 00:26:22,760
and recruit these female refugees?

533
00:26:23,000 --> 00:26:23,600
This way,

534
00:26:23,720 --> 00:26:25,280
not only will they fill up
the manpower vacancy,

535
00:26:25,480 --> 00:26:26,960
they'll also be taught a skill.

536
00:26:27,200 --> 00:26:28,720
When they go back to their hometown

537
00:26:28,840 --> 00:26:30,080
after this disaster,

538
00:26:30,200 --> 00:26:32,680
they'll also have a skill
to earn a living.

539
00:26:34,200 --> 00:26:35,480
In that case,

540
00:26:35,600 --> 00:26:37,000
that's a good idea.

541
00:26:37,480 --> 00:26:38,320
Even if the details

542
00:26:38,400 --> 00:26:39,600
still need to be ironed out,

543
00:26:39,720 --> 00:26:40,840
it's very feasible.

544
00:26:41,000 --> 00:26:41,840
That's one merit for you.

545
00:26:44,240 --> 00:26:45,280
What should I reward you with?

546
00:26:45,800 --> 00:26:47,320
I just randomly thought about it.

547
00:26:47,440 --> 00:26:48,360
I don't deserve a reward.

548
00:26:48,760 --> 00:26:51,080
You handle things in a proper manner,
and you know how to give and take.

549
00:26:51,520 --> 00:26:52,560
If you were a man,

550
00:26:52,920 --> 00:26:54,120
you'd surely accomplish great things.

551
00:26:55,080 --> 00:26:55,760
Can't a woman

552
00:26:55,880 --> 00:26:57,280
accomplish great things too?

553
00:27:07,680 --> 00:27:08,400
My Lord.

554
00:27:11,880 --> 00:27:12,600
The sunlight is glaring.

555
00:27:12,720 --> 00:27:13,600
I didn't see anything.

556
00:27:13,720 --> 00:27:14,440
I'll leave right away.

557
00:27:14,960 --> 00:27:15,760
Don't go.

558
00:27:15,880 --> 00:27:17,040
I'm just preparing to leave.

559
00:27:21,720 --> 00:27:22,920
I've already got your size.

560
00:27:23,000 --> 00:27:23,560
I'll make

561
00:27:23,680 --> 00:27:25,000
the new clothes as soon as I can.

562
00:27:25,560 --> 00:27:26,600
I'll go ahead.

563
00:27:29,320 --> 00:27:29,920
Your Ladyship.

564
00:27:31,160 --> 00:27:32,600
This is jasmine flower tea
given by His Majesty.

565
00:27:32,840 --> 00:27:33,880
