There's no need to feel that way.

844
00:38:56,840 --> 00:38:57,680
Just tell His Lordship

845
00:38:57,840 --> 00:38:59,800
that I said so. I can't take
undeserved rewards.

846
00:39:01,200 --> 00:39:02,120
Well said.

847
00:39:03,960 --> 00:39:04,720
My Lord.

848
00:39:05,840 --> 00:39:06,560
My Lord.

849
00:39:07,640 --> 00:39:08,640
Don't forget.

850
00:39:08,960 --> 00:39:10,320
As the Xu family's matron,

851
00:39:10,640 --> 00:39:11,880
It's unavoidable

852
00:39:12,080 --> 00:39:13,840
to meet guests and entertain them.

853
00:39:14,280 --> 00:39:15,400
If people see

854
00:39:15,560 --> 00:39:16,680
that you don't have money,

855
00:39:17,000 --> 00:39:18,600
I'm the one who will be embarrassed.

856
00:39:19,800 --> 00:39:21,640
Besides, you made a huge accomplishment

857
00:39:21,840 --> 00:39:23,400
for the Xu family regarding
the disaster relief.

858
00:39:23,640 --> 00:39:25,560
Why do you say
that you don't deserve a reward?

859
00:39:26,600 --> 00:39:27,640
Yes, Your Ladyship.

860
00:39:27,800 --> 00:39:29,560
I think what His Lordship said
makes sense.

861
00:39:29,720 --> 00:39:31,320
You have many things
to take care of in the future.

862
00:39:31,480 --> 00:39:32,680
Money makes the world go round.

863
00:39:36,640 --> 00:39:37,680
In that case,

864
00:39:37,880 --> 00:39:39,000
I'll accept it.

865
00:39:39,160 --> 00:39:40,600
Thank you for your kindness.

866
00:39:57,200 --> 00:39:58,280
You have more money

867
00:39:58,280 --> 00:39:59,280
to give to me?

868
00:39:59,400 --> 00:40:00,480
Take a look yourself.

869
00:40:07,560 --> 00:40:08,560
These are...

870
00:40:09,880 --> 00:40:11,320
For the sake of the disaster relief,

871
00:40:11,520 --> 00:40:14,240
you used these land titles
to gather rice.

872
00:40:15,200 --> 00:40:16,360
You were decisive,

873
00:40:16,560 --> 00:40:17,960
and resolved the crisis for the Xu family.

874
00:40:18,160 --> 00:40:19,080
I appreciate it very much.

875
00:40:20,200 --> 00:40:22,560
But you shouldn't use your dowry

876
00:40:22,800 --> 00:40:24,480
to support the Xu family.

877
00:40:26,200 --> 00:40:27,360
However,

878
00:40:27,760 --> 00:40:29,240
why are there more land titles?

879
00:40:30,480 --> 00:40:31,960
Your lands

880
00:40:32,480 --> 00:40:33,640
were scattered.

881
00:40:33,840 --> 00:40:35,160
They're mostly not good farmlands.

882
00:40:35,520 --> 00:40:36,680
I told Steward Bai

883
00:40:36,880 --> 00:40:37,920
to buy the farmlands

884
00:40:38,120 --> 00:40:39,280
around them as well,

885
00:40:39,800 --> 00:40:41,680
so that your scattered farmlands

886
00:40:41,880 --> 00:40:42,640
will be connected together.

887
00:40:42,920 --> 00:40:44,240
The harvest will be better too.

888
00:40:44,960 --> 00:40:45,920
My Lord.

889
00:40:46,520 --> 00:40:48,120
I was just doing what I should.

890
00:40:48,440 --> 00:40:49,600
You spent a lot of money.

891
00:40:50,560 --> 00:40:51,560
We're husband and wife.

892
00:40:52,000 --> 00:40:53,200
Why do you act like an outsider?

893
00:41:03,440 --> 00:41:04,040
Zhaoying.

894
00:41:04,920 --> 00:41:06,200
I'm not going back to have lunch.

895
00:41:06,520 --> 00:41:08,560
I'll eat here today.

896
00:41:09,600 --> 00:41:10,800
Yes, My Lord.

897
00:41:20,600 --> 00:41:21,400
Wait.

898
00:41:28,040 --> 00:41:29,560
Why are all these sweet?

899
00:41:30,360 --> 00:41:32,040
Her Ladyship likes
the sour and sweet taste,

900
00:41:32,200 --> 00:41:32,880
so the kitchen

901
00:41:33,080 --> 00:41:34,800
would usually send these
to Western Lateral Court.

902
00:41:36,520 --> 00:41:37,840
Go and tell the kitchen

903
00:41:38,000 --> 00:41:38,800
to make other dishes.

904
00:41:39,000 --> 00:41:40,800
I'm afraid His Lordship aren't
used to these.

905
00:41:41,040 --> 00:41:41,720
Yes.

906
00:41:55,640 --> 00:41:56,840
My Lord, I'm sorry.

907
00:41:57,040 --> 00:41:59,240
I like Yuhang dishes,

908
00:41:59,440 --> 00:42:01,280
so these are what the kitchen prepared.

909
00:42:01,480 --> 00:42:02,280
But I've already asked them

910
00:42:02,480 --> 00:42:04,080
to prepare the dishes you like.

911
00:42:05,320 --> 00:42:06,640
I suddenly decided to eat here
at the last minute.

912
00:42:06,840 --> 00:42:07,520
It's not your fault.

913
00:42:09,760 --> 00:42:11,400
Then, My Lord,

914
00:42:11,880 --> 00:42:13,800
try this sweet and sour fish.

915
00:42:17,040 --> 00:42:18,960
Why would anyone like dishes

916
00:42:19,160 --> 00:42:21,440
made from syrup?

917
00:42:21,880 --> 00:42:22,960
If someone likes it,

918
00:42:23,120 --> 00:42:24,880
that means it has its good point.

919
00:42:26,280 --> 00:42:27,040
Tell me about that.

920
00:42:28,920 --> 00:42:29,920
This sugar and vinegar sauce

921
00:42:30,120 --> 00:42:32,240
is where the essence of this dish lies.

922
00:42:32,920 --> 00:42:34,000
Regardless if it's the heat

923
00:42:34,160 --> 00:42:35,480
or the speed of cooking this dish,

924
00:42:35,680 --> 00:42:37,280
they must be just right.

925
00:42:42,560 --> 00:42:43,280
It's delicious.

926
00:42:47,320 --> 00:42:50,000
This fish looks very ordinary.

927
00:42:50,440 --> 00:42:51,680
Why do you like it?

928
00:42:51,960 --> 00:42:52,840
Because it's delicious.

929
00:42:53,680 --> 00:42:54,640
And look.

930
00:42:54,880 --> 00:42:56,600
It's a very ordinary food.

931
00:42:56,840 --> 00:42:59,320
Yet after precise and careful cooking,

932
00:42:59,520 --> 00:43:00,080
it became

933
00:43:00,240 --> 00:43:01,680
a unique flavor.

934
00:43:02,640 --> 00:43:03,640
And I think

935
00:43:03,840 --> 00:43:04,960
that in many things,

936
00:43:05,160 --> 00:43:06,600
it doesn't matter
if it's expensive or not.

937
00:43:07,120 --> 00:43:08,440
Even if it's just very simple,

938
00:43:08,640 --> 00:43:10,240
as long as we make an effort
to notice it,

939
00:43:10,600 --> 00:43:12,720
it has its unforgettable aspects.

940
00:43:13,560 --> 00:43:16,040
When all things started,
complicated things were unbelievably simple.

941
00:43:16,800 --> 00:43:17,400
One dish

942
00:43:17,600 --> 00:43:19,800
can even make you realize
important things in life.

943
00:43:37,280 --> 00:43:37,960
How does it taste?

944
00:43:41,040 --> 00:43:42,240
It's sour, sweet and delicious.

945
00:43:42,840 --> 00:43:45,200
It's unique indeed.

946
00:43:46,680 --> 00:43:47,520
Then try

947
00:43:47,680 --> 00:43:48,760
this Longjing shrimp.

948
00:43:59,200 --> 00:43:59,800
Not bad.

949
00:44:05,480 --> 00:44:06,680
It's fine. We have enough dishes.

950
00:44:06,880 --> 00:44:07,480
You may go.

951
00:44:10,080 --> 00:44:10,520
By the way,

952
00:44:10,840 --> 00:44:12,040
how are the clothes

953
00:44:12,040 --> 00:44:12,720
you're making for me progressing?

954
00:44:13,960 --> 00:44:14,440
(Oh, no.)

955
00:44:14,720 --> 00:44:16,480
(I just made a casual remark back then.)

956
00:44:16,680 --> 00:44:18,080
(I didn't expect
that he'd still remember.)

957
00:44:18,600 --> 00:44:20,200
I'm still making them.

958
00:44:20,400 --> 00:44:21,520
If you're in a hurry,

959
00:44:21,720 --> 00:44:22,920
I'll finish them in the next few days

960
00:44:23,120 --> 00:44:23,960
and bring them to you.

961
00:44:24,520 --> 00:44:25,120
It's fine.

962
00:44:26,400 --> 00:44:27,480
I just

963
00:44:28,160 --> 00:44:29,800
haven't worn new clothes for a while.

964
00:44:31,680 --> 00:44:33,040
You're well-built.

965
00:44:33,240 --> 00:44:34,560
You'd look good in anything you wear.

966
00:44:43,880 --> 00:44:45,400
Didn't Great Madam

967
00:44:45,600 --> 00:44:47,240
just send a couple
of clothes over yesterday?

968
00:45:02,040 --> 00:45:03,440
(You're well-built.)

969
00:45:03,520 --> 00:45:04,760
(You'd look good in anything you wear.)

970
00:45:10,840 --> 00:45:11,400
My Lord.

971
00:45:12,240 --> 00:45:14,680
Is there anything wrong
with these clothes?

972
00:45:17,280 --> 00:45:18,120
It's fine.

973
00:45:19,280 --> 00:45:20,120
Why did you come here?

974
00:45:20,320 --> 00:45:21,680
Dinner is ready.

975
00:45:33,040 --> 00:45:34,360
Sweet and sour fish?

976
00:45:35,200 --> 00:45:37,600
I saw how happy you were
when you had it at lunch,

977
00:45:37,800 --> 00:45:39,400
so I asked the kitchen to make it.

978
00:45:39,560 --> 00:45:41,000
If you don't like it,

979
00:45:41,160 --> 00:45:42,080
I'll take it away.

980
00:46:04,400 --> 00:46:05,280
It's delicious.

981
00:46:07,920 --> 00:46:08,760
It doesn't taste right.

982
00:46:09,320 --> 00:46:10,520
The same cook

983
00:46:10,720 --> 00:46:11,840
made the sweet and sour fish dish

984
00:46:12,000 --> 00:46:13,560
for Her Ladyship at lunch time.

985
00:46:15,520 --> 00:46:16,360
Take it away.

986
00:46:20,960 --> 00:46:24,160
I think what you liked wasn't the fish,

987
00:46:24,360 --> 00:46:27,160
but the one you ate it with.

988
00:46:41,320 --> 00:46:42,080
My Lord.

989
00:46:43,440 --> 00:46:44,440
Bad news.

990
00:47:01,760 --> 00:47:04,480
♪In the cold darkness of midnight,
a sigh is heard♪

991
00:47:05,120 --> 00:47:07,880
♪Who picked up the paintbrush
to draw loneliness♪

992
00:47:09,200 --> 00:47:15,760
♪In my life, I can draw everything,
but lovesickness♪

993
00:47:16,200 --> 00:47:18,240
♪The mountain city is waiting for rain♪

994
00:47:19,240 --> 00:47:22,840
♪I am waiting for you
to pass in my memory♪

995
00:47:23,280 --> 00:47:29,440
♪The sky is in a more lonely color
than your face♪

996
00:47:29,880 --> 00:47:32,400
♪The wind rises
and the candle light flickers♪

997
00:47:33,320 --> 00:47:35,880
♪The thin clothes
can't stand the cold days♪

998
00:47:37,080 --> 00:47:43,920
♪Full of twists and turns,
fate is untold♪

999
00:47:44,320 --> 00:47:46,520
♪I ground my thoughts into ink♪

1000
00:47:47,520 --> 00:47:50,960
♪But I still can't sketch your contours♪

1001
00:47:51,480 --> 00:47:57,240
♪How could the ink
and paper exhaust our stories♪

1002
00:47:58,080 --> 00:48:04,960
♪Who picked up the pen
to disturb the heart♪

1003
00:48:05,320 --> 00:48:11,960
♪Who visited to remind me of the past♪

1004
00:48:12,360 --> 00:48:15,680
♪If feelings can be kept in mind,
but cannot be confessed♪

1005
00:48:17,040 --> 00:48:19,080
♪I won't escape from whatever end♪

1006
00:48:20,560 --> 00:48:26,280
♪In the dim lantern light,
with you there is me♪

1007
00:48:26,280 --> 00:48:33,200
♪Who picked up the pen
to set free lonely tears♪

1008
00:48:33,440 --> 00:48:39,960
♪Whoever visited my life,
only you stayed all the days♪

1009
00:48:40,520 --> 00:48:44,040
♪If the moth doesn't fly into the fire♪

1010
00:48:45,120 --> 00:48:48,080
♪How can it be said to be persistent♪

1011
00:48:48,560 --> 00:48:56,200
♪Coming to the end of your story,
there is me♪
